                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270215-31-victim268 t18270215-31-viclabel161"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18270215-31-crimeloc162">Newgate-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270215-31-crimeloc162" type="placeName" value="Newgate-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18270215-31-crimeloc162" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270215-31-off159 t18270215-31-crimeloc162"></join>. I was informed the prisoner had taken a fowl from my shop; I went, and found her two doors off - brought her back, and found a dead fowl under her cloak; I had seen it shortly before in the middle of the shop; she said it was not mine for she had bought it of a strange man for 2s.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270215-31-person269">
                  MOSES 
                  COHEN
