            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner; she was crying; she told the alderman she had bought it, but did not say so before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270215-31-person270">
                  JOHN 
                  GEARING
               <interp inst="t18270215-31-person270" type="surname" value="GEARING"></interp>
