                     <interp inst="t18270215-31-person270" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I sell fowls and rabbits, and live in the Borough. I was in Mr. Bowles's shop - I saw the prisoner come in and take this fowl from a lot, and go out without paying; I told Mr. Bowles, who brought her back with it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I bought this fowl of a woman for 2s. 3d., meaning to make a person a present of it - I went into the prosecutor's shop to ask the price of a pig.</p>
               <p>MR. BOWLES. I had no pig in my shop.</p>
